{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The game</h2>Nature is harsh. Only the most adapted will survive. Following a thorough study of nature, Loophole Interactive is proud to bring you King of the Couch: Zoovival! Take up the role as one of nature's toughest zoovivors as they battle it out using tools commonly found in nature, such as a black hole gun. Save yourself from a cheese wheel running amok by swinging yourself to safety using a grappling hook. Chug baguettes at your friends under the wrathful eyes of a pissed of volcano. All part of natural selection!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2D battle platformer with 3D graphics<br></li><li>Up to 4 players versus eachother<br></li><li>Use a grappling hook to move around<br></li><li>Lots of funky weapons commonly found in nature<br></li><li>All-natural, realistic weapon-classes<br></li><li>Play as a bear, a fish, a frog, chicken, penguin, toothless t-rex, or a sewing lady<br></li><li>Various arenas with game-changing mechanics</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Around the world!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/724350/8e26b0321c0c2d720cf2e98214816e5b813f903f.jpg"},{"name":"So Classic!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/724350/e7e20f15347581db15160de603d55014de0d92d2.jpg"},{"name":"Too many cooks spoil the soup.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/724350/6edb96a880ca90304aab653c64b8717e7f87d9a6.jpg"},{"name":"Nani?!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/724350/cd7cd198469ddb8f26fe407c053b656eb47665b1.jpg"},{"name":"I got a PHD in PvP.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/724350/dcfcf7d4815543c83561d04898c5df96fef1668b.jpg"},{"name":"Under construction.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/724350/5572cccc8830c406f9a022ded9927079